		<title><![CDATA[The Top Five Celebrities at Our Dream Party Barge]]></title>
		<link>https://premierpartycruises.com/blog/the-top-five-celebrities-at-our-dream-party-barge/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:10:22 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[JosePilapil]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://premierpartycruises.com/the-top-five-celebrities-at-our-dream-party-barge/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>The Top Five Celebrities at Our Dream Party Barge
</h1>				
		The Best Guest List for a Premier Party Disco Cruise in Austin, Texas		
															<img width="1140" height="760" src="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-5.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-5.jpg 1140w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" />					
		<p>There comes a time in every person's life when they must ask themselves serious questions in order to navigate the modern world we live in. This is a normal part of a human's intellectual development process and should not be taken lightly. We believe that as a party boat company operating out of Lake Travis in Austin, Texas, where we rent out private pontoon boats but also specialize in our FAMOUS DISCO CRUISE PARTY events for bachelor and bachelorette parties that it makes sense for us to weigh in on this issue and lend some thought leadership to the subject.</p>		
															<img width="1140" height="828" src="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-2.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-2.jpg 1140w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-2-300x218.jpg 300w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-2-768x558.jpg 768w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-2-1024x744.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" />					
		<p>We've thought about it so you don't have to and can you believe someone actually gets paid to write this, here we go!</p>		
					<h2>BRITNEY SPEARS. 
</h2>				
		<p>I mean…here is the thing. She loves to dance so she is, without a doubt, going to get that party boat dance floor BOPPING while our DJs are doing what they do best and cultivating vibes, as they do. She is unpredictable and frequently nude-but peaceful (unless we also invited her family on board which, we would NEVER so not a problem). This makes her our number 1 dream boat party attendee due to sheer entertainment factors combined with a small level of fear from the innate unpredictability. Plus we could use the publicity.</p>		
															<img width="1140" height="760" src="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-3.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-3.jpg 1140w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" />					
					<h2>BILL MURRAY. 
</h2>				
		<p>Need we explain further? He's the ultimate party starter, facilitator, and until the last minute he is on point until we dock back at Anderson Mill Marina and the party is over. He gets along with everyone, he is calm, he is funny, he loves life and we believe he would also follow the boat rules, especially now that he is older. We aren't sure if we could handle young Bill Murray, he may have had to sign a special kind of waiver to protect us from that kind of liability. Also, he doesn't ask for much, just some good vibes, some laughs, and maybe some tasty snacks which is basically what we are all about. </p>		
					<h2> MARTHA STEWART.
</h2>				
		<p>Ok hear us out. You look at her and you think, "what's up" older conservative lady? But then, it's Martha Stewart and it is an older conservative lady but she's high, has prison stories and is right there in the mix with you making jokes, chatting, a with and entire tray of GOURMET SANDWICHES dressed with cute little wrappers. We mean, like, the kind of sandwiches that have artisanal homemade bread and fancy things like grey poupon or whatever. All kinds of sandwich upgrades PLUS amazing stories and life advice. We're definitely fascinated by the potential here, even though we're not entirely sure what a Martha Stewart party boat experience would be like.</p>		
					<h2>LIZZO. 
</h2>				
		<p>The vibes, the singing, the charisma, the confidence, the FUN. I mean, come on! We are a party boat company and Lizzo is basically a celebration that walks around in human form. She's a superstar performer with great energy that would keep that boat party ROCKING while we party cruise around Lake Travis. She's also very Austin, Texas coded so we think there would be a natural fit there. Plus we think she would love our disco cruise parties and might put us in a music video? We can dream, right? </p>		
															<img width="1140" height="760" src="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-4.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-4.jpg 1140w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-4-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" />					
					<h2>MATTHEW MCCONAUGHEY.
</h2>				
		<p>Well, we had to include him on the list- he's from Austin! We think he would be chill, keep the vibes at an appropriate level and would be good for conversation. He would also help keep the party going by being generally friendly and charming but not in an overbearing way. Also, we think he would enjoy our beautiful lake and help everyone appreciate the natural beauty of what we get to see every day. Plus, there's a decent change he knows some of the better boat captain spots on the lake which could lead to a fun exploration boat adventure?</p>		
															<img width="1140" height="760" src="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-1.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-1.jpg 1140w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://premierpartycruises.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/austin-texas-blog-top-five-celebrities-image-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1140px) 100vw, 1140px" />					
		<p>Alright, alright, alright. These are some of the celebrities we think would fit well with the Premier Party Cruises experience and help create some truly memorable experiences on our Lake Travis party boat. Of course, we are open to collaborating with anyone that appreciates good times, great music, and beautiful scenery! Feel free to get in touch if any of you celebrities are reading this and want to book a private cruise or join us for one of our disco cruise events!</p>		
		<p>In the meantime, if you are interested in booking one of our party boats for your own special event, whether it's a bachelor party, bachelorette party, corporate event, or any other kind of celebration, please reach out to us and we'll help you create an unforgettable experience on Lake Travis!</p>				
											</content:encoded>
